The adopted scheme for full-space device design optimization is sequential as shown in Fig. 2. It is composed of two parts. The first one is the device simulation module, where there are many convenient tools38; as aforementioned, in this work, SCAPS is used. Giving two input vectors v∈ℝN\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
